Description: Fragment of tall ring foot of Attic black-glazed small pottery open vase. Wholly glazed. Incised inscription on underside.

Bernand 1970 / Le Delta égyptien d'après les textes grecs, i: les confins libyques (p. 673, no. 317)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GA.1598)
